### **Title:**
```
GenAi Aggressive Portfolio: Weekly Performance Review – Quantum Investor Digest
```

### **Introduction (Standard - Use Every Week):**
```
On October 9, 2025, I launched my journey with GenAi—a transformer-based 
generative AI model specializing in dynamic stock analysis—to build and 
manage an aggressive portfolio designed to beat the S&P 500. Every Thursday 
after market close, I document the progress, insights, and actionable 
recommendations to empower tech-savvy and institutional investors.
```

