## **Benchmark Tracking**

### **Primary Benchmark:**
- **S&P 500 Index (^GSPC)**
- Inception value: 6,688 (Oct 9, 2025)
- Track weekly closes
- Calculate total return from inception

### **Secondary Benchmark:**
- **Bitcoin (BTC-USD)**
- Inception value: $123,353 (Oct 9, 2025)
- Track weekly closes
- Use as alternative asset comparison

### **Performance Metrics to Track:**
- Weekly change %
- Total return since Oct 9
- Excess return vs S&P 500
- Volatility (standard deviation of weekly returns)
- Maximum drawdown from peak
- Win rate (% of weeks with positive returns)

